    },
    "description": {
      "value": "<div><p>You teleport up to 60 feet to an unoccupied space you can see. On each of your turns before the spell ends, you can use a bonus action to teleport in this way again.</p><div><p>Additionally, while under the effects of this spell, you can use your reaction to teleport 10 feet to an unoccupied space you can see if a creature makes an attack roll against you. If you are still in reach or range of the attack then it is made at disadvantage against you.</p><p><strong>At Higher Levels.</strong> Using a spell slot of 9th level or higher grants a duration that does not require concentration.</p></div></div>",
